"c04db4a027e2a54ce028a55213eaaa490b080f60","tid":1370782,"uid":113071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"漢仔好波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"梁粉都好波，多謝助功，CY定必出山做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄭國漢被部分人認為有著親梁振英的政治背景，因此遭到了嶺南大學學生會的質疑，並反對鄭國漢出任嶺南大學校長，嶺南大學學生會不排除發起罷課抗議<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「梁粉」</span></span></strong>（梁振英的支持者）鄭國漢出任嶺南大學校長。而鄭國漢上任後對部分學者採取高壓措施，例如他於2014年向大學中文系助理教授陳雲根公開發出警告信，批評他的言行與學者身分相悖，超越言論自由的底線，嚴重影響嶺大校譽。及後於2016年決定不和陳續約。"},{"pid":"ac0ddcc8e48f888416add678cf24d45db84931e9","tid":1370782,"uid":182715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7b9c352ad974c7b4ed4ec9e1e32834d792b0b0","tid":1370782,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:52:19.000Z","msg":"港大支畜校腸食屎啦"},{"pid":"7792afba65e56a45b1299585f9d2e38457d918b3","tid":1370782,"uid":199081,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"70097d01feb738876c7f8a2a21c5a79583774158","tid":1370782,"uid":109923,"like":150,"dislike":0,"score":150,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"叫佢譴責唔肯<br />\n叫佢定開會日期調查何妖唔肯<br />\n出d各打50大板要非暴力聲明<br />\n比人陰佢話要非暴力，咁落元朗保護學生<br />\n最後屈服群眾壓力先肯落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"群眾壓力下低頭真係好難<br />\n林奠唔肯講撤回<br />\n警救唔肯道歉<br />\n呢次鄭國漢就算做戲觀察 都起碼叫做得好睇"},{"pid":"e62fc5b4ad50749355876558c01f2cf1d5bfdcac","tid":1370782,"uid":278911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"贏咗，一大實至名歸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac